# Pinned agent image versions (2026.<m>.<d>-g<sha> — consistent with the deploy versioning). Sourced by
# agents/{agent-session,coordinator-session,reviewer-session}.sh; also mirrored (pinned literal) in
# agents/coordinator/review-reflex.yaml. Bumped by the image repos' deploy-pin PRs (agent-runtime →
# AGENT_BASE_IMAGE, agent-coordinator → AGENT_COORDINATOR_IMAGE). Pinned (NOT :latest) → k8s uses
# imagePullPolicy IfNotPresent by default (no pullAlways), cacheable, traceable to the build commit.
AGENT_BASE_IMAGE=ghcr.io/teststuffstash/agent-base:2026.7.6-g7908e5c8cd63
AGENT_COORDINATOR_IMAGE=ghcr.io/teststuffstash/agent-coordinator:2026.7.6-g24480c99a3ea
